Package: uniaxialOptics
Version: 0.1
Date: 2008-07-08
Title: Modelling multilayer anisotropic stacks
Author: Steph Cornford <eltadcirad@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Steph Cornford <eltadcirad@gmail.com>
Suggests: EricksenLeslie
Description: Computes transmission and/or reflection through
             a 1D optical uniaxial stack, such as a liquid crystal cell. 
             Available methods: Ko variant of Berremans 4x4 Matrix Method,
	     	                Lien variant of Extended Jones Method
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: http://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/photonics/
